<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>主页</title>
    <link href="~/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link href="~/css/jquery.seat-charts.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link href="~/css/index_q.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link href="~/css/jquery.seat-charts.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <script src="~/js/time.js"></script>
    <script src="~/js/seat.js"></script>
    <script src="~/js/inedex_q.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
    <!--顶部log-->
    <div class="container" id="log">
        <div class="topFont">
            <a href="#">
                <img alt="图片丢失" src="~/Content/themes/base/images/log5.jpg" />
            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="topFont ml">
            <a href="#">
                <img alt="图片丢失" src="~/Content/themes/base/images/kjyy.png" />
            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="topFont ml">
            <p><span>欢迎进行选座，现在是</span></p>
            <p><span id="current-time">2017/12/22 下午6:30:30</span></p>
            <p><span>可预约座位数1000</span></p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <!--左侧功能导航-->
    <div class="container col-lg-1 col-lg-offset-2">
        <ul class="nav nav-pills nav-stacked">
            <li role="presentation" class="active" id="li1"><a href="#">预约<br />座位</a></li>
            <li role="presentation" id="li2"><a href="#">预约<br />信息</a></li>
            <li role="presentation" id="li3"><a href="#">退出<br />系统</a></li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <!--系统公告-->
    <div class="container col-lg-offset-1" id="gg" style="border: 1px solid crimson; float:left;height: auto;width: 26%;">系统公告：无</div>
    <!--选择座位功能-->
    <div class="container middle" id="htm1">
        <div id="seat-map"><div class="front1">北</div></div>
        <div class="booking-details">
            <p><span style="color: #5bc0de">小明</span>同学，</p>
            <p>选择你的预约时间和座位</p>
            <div>
                <form>
                    <p class="font2">房间：</p>
                    <select class="cClass font2">
                        <option>图书馆一楼101</option>
                        <option>图书馆一楼102</option>
                        <option>图书馆二楼201</option>
                        <option>图书馆二楼202</option>
                        <option>图书馆三楼301</option>
                        <option>图书馆三楼302</option>
                        <option>图书馆四楼401</option>
                        <option>图书馆四楼402</option>
                    </select>
                    <p class="font2">选择时间：</p>
                    <select class="cTimeDay font2">
                        <option><span id="showDay"></span></option>
                        <option>明天1月5号</option>
                        <option>后天1月6号</option>
                    </select>
                    <p class="font2">选择时段：</p>
                    <select class="cTime font2">
                        <option>7:00-8:00</option>
                        <option>8:00-9:00</option>
                        <option>9:00-10:00</option>
                        <option>10:00-11:00</option>
                        <option>11:00-12:00</option>
                        <option>12:00-13:00</option>
                        <option>13:00-14:00</option>
                        <option>14:00-15:00</option>
                        <option>15:00-16:00</option>
                        <option>16:00-17:00</option>
                        <option>17:00-18:00</option>
                        <option>18:00-19:00</option>
                        <option>19:00-20:00</option>
                        <option>20:00-21:00</option>
                        <option>21:00-22:00</option>
                    </select>
                </form>
            </div>
            <p>座位：</p>
            <!--显示选择的座位-->
            <ul id="selected-seats"></ul>
            <button type="submit" class="checkout-button">确定</button>
            <div id="legend"></div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <!--预约信息管理功能-->
    <div class="container middle" id="htm2">
        <p>注意：目前系统延时只支持半个小时为基数哦！</p>
        <p><span style="color: #5bc0de">小明</span>同学，</p>
        <p>选择你的预约时间:<span class="myTime"></span></p>
        <p>选择你的开始时间:<span class="myTime"></span></p>
        <p>选择你的结束时间:<span class="myTime"></span></p>
        <p>选择你预约的座位:<span class="mySeat"></span></p>
        <input type="submit" value="取消续约">
        <input type="submit" value="延长时间">
    </div>
    <!--底部-->
    <div class="container text-center col-lg-8 col-lg-offset-2">
        <address>
            <strong>&#169;文华学院</strong><br>
            湖北省，武汉市，洪山区<br>
            关山街道，文园路8号
            <abbr title="联系电话">Tel:027-87599065</abbr>
            <p>技术支持：<a href="">引航工作室</a></p>
        </address>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
